WEBVTT

00:00:44.362 --> 00:00:49.137
=The Hidden Heir Ye Chen=
(Adapted from "The Peerless Son-in-Law")

00:00:49.650 --> 00:00:52.225
=Episode 26=

00:00:53.200 --> 00:00:53.920
Here, Ms. Lan.

00:00:54.520 --> 00:00:55.759
I brought you

00:00:55.759 --> 00:00:56.719
some fruits.

00:00:57.000 --> 00:00:58.520
A friend of mine lives here too.

00:00:58.799 --> 00:01:00.119
She invited me over for mahjong.

00:01:01.320 --> 00:01:03.079
Wait, you have friends who live here?

00:01:04.840 --> 00:01:06.039
I met her at the table.

00:01:06.399 --> 00:01:07.159
She's loaded.

00:01:07.399 --> 00:01:08.200
I mean, filthy rich.

00:01:08.679 --> 00:01:10.319
She loves a few rounds of mahjong.

00:01:11.159 --> 00:01:12.637
She's garbage at it, though.

00:01:12.650 --> 00:01:14.040
She's just in it for the fun anyway.

00:01:14.400 --> 00:01:15.319
She'll lose six figures

00:01:15.560 --> 00:01:17.400
and won't even flinch.

00:01:18.079 --> 00:01:18.519
Alright.

00:01:19.400 --> 00:01:20.519
I should get going now.

00:01:20.879 --> 00:01:22.640
I've got a game to get to.

00:01:24.120 --> 00:01:24.959
Hongyan, wait.

00:01:25.400 --> 00:01:26.840
Yeah? What is it, Ms. Lan?

00:01:27.480 --> 00:01:29.239
I'm just sitting around at home anyway.

00:01:29.680 --> 00:01:31.040
You guys need a fourth?

00:01:31.480 --> 00:01:32.159
Count me in.

00:01:33.840 --> 00:01:35.359
Ugh, I'm such an idiot.

00:01:35.760 --> 00:01:37.439
How did I not think of you?

00:01:38.239 --> 00:01:39.680
If we team up

00:01:39.959 --> 00:01:40.920
and feed each other

00:01:40.920 --> 00:01:41.680
the right tiles,

00:01:42.319 --> 00:01:43.879
we'll totally clean house.

00:01:44.640 --> 00:01:45.040
Exactly.

00:01:47.359 --> 00:01:49.560
This is Lian. I've told you about her.

00:01:50.000 --> 00:01:50.719
And this is Qiang.

00:01:51.187 --> 00:01:52.537
They're my regulars.

00:01:52.850 --> 00:01:53.959
Everyone, this is my bestie,

00:01:53.959 --> 00:01:54.560
Lan.

00:01:54.959 --> 00:01:55.560
Lan, huh?

00:01:55.680 --> 00:01:56.612
Are you a good sport?

00:01:56.799 --> 00:01:57.560
Totally.

00:01:57.719 --> 00:01:59.640
Lan, it's our first time playing together.

00:01:59.959 --> 00:02:01.400
Let's start low at 1,000.

00:02:01.719 --> 00:02:03.200
Can we agree on a 64-fold cap?

00:02:04.230 --> 00:02:05.640
The maximum payout is over 60,000.

00:02:05.799 --> 00:02:07.712
Do you usually play
for stakes this high?

00:02:07.799 --> 00:02:08.200
Yeah.

00:02:08.200 --> 00:02:09.287
You call this high?

00:02:09.500 --> 00:02:11.225
This is the smallest stake
we've ever played.

00:02:11.225 --> 00:02:12.239
Normally, we're doing

00:02:12.359 --> 00:02:13.359
3,000 to 5,000 a hand.

00:02:14.039 --> 00:02:15.159
Sometimes over 10,000.

00:02:15.360 --> 00:02:16.000
Right.

00:02:16.400 --> 00:02:17.479
If it's too much for you,

00:02:17.650 --> 00:02:18.680
we can just skip it today.

00:02:19.439 --> 00:02:20.080
No, don't.

00:02:20.599 --> 00:02:21.719
I didn't mean anything.

00:02:21.879 --> 00:02:22.639
I can do 1,000.

00:02:22.840 --> 00:02:23.800
Let's stick with that.

00:02:24.080 --> 00:02:24.840
It's nothing crazy.

00:02:25.319 --> 00:02:26.100
Let's get into it.

00:02:34.639 --> 00:02:35.759
We'll use hand signals

00:02:35.960 --> 00:02:37.080
to coordinate once we start.

00:02:37.560 --> 00:02:39.240
Touching the nose means Bamboos.

00:02:39.599 --> 00:02:41.080
Tucking hair means Cracks.

00:02:41.719 --> 00:02:43.240
Pursing lips means Dots.

00:02:48.759 --> 00:02:49.319
Three Bamboo.

00:02:50.120 --> 00:02:50.599
Run.

00:02:51.199 --> 00:02:51.960
I'm ready to win.

00:02:52.680 --> 00:02:54.000
Already?

00:02:54.280 --> 00:02:55.560
I better not feed you your win.

00:02:56.080 --> 00:02:56.570
Four Crack.

00:02:57.039 --> 00:02:57.560
Two Crack.

00:02:58.199 --> 00:02:59.280
I win!

00:03:00.080 --> 00:03:00.840
Are you kidding me?

00:03:01.240 --> 00:03:02.199
Talk about a jinx.

00:03:02.360 --> 00:03:03.680
Hey, we had a deal.

00:03:03.680 --> 00:03:04.759
Pay up. No whining.

00:03:05.039 --> 00:03:06.360
What do you take me for?

00:03:06.625 --> 00:03:08.800
A 24-fold win. That's 24,000.

00:03:10.800 --> 00:03:11.639
Check it yourself.

00:03:12.039 --> 00:03:13.240
Ms. Lian, you're a class act.

00:03:13.479 --> 00:03:13.960
Come on.

00:03:14.159 --> 00:03:14.919
Another round.

00:03:14.919 --> 00:03:15.879
Let's keep it moving.

00:03:21.599 --> 00:03:22.080
Nine Crack.

00:03:22.319 --> 00:03:22.919
I win.

00:03:23.759 --> 00:03:24.280
Soap.

00:03:24.560 --> 00:03:25.319
I win.

00:03:26.919 --> 00:03:27.400
Hidden Quad.

00:03:27.520 --> 00:03:27.960
Run.

00:03:28.639 --> 00:03:28.960
Set.

00:03:29.400 --> 00:03:29.840
That's it.

00:03:30.240 --> 00:03:30.639
I win.

00:03:30.919 --> 00:03:31.759
I win again.

00:03:31.800 --> 00:03:32.919
Man, I'm on a roll.

00:03:35.280 --> 00:03:35.840
Wow, Ms. Lan.

00:03:36.439 --> 00:03:37.800
Your luck is insane.

00:03:38.159 --> 00:03:39.240
In just a few rounds,

00:03:39.240 --> 00:03:40.570
you've taken us for over 300,000.

00:03:40.879 --> 00:03:42.975
Guess today's your day.

00:03:43.159 --> 00:03:44.199
You guys went easy on me.

00:03:45.039 --> 00:03:46.840
Look, these 1,000 stakes are a joke.

00:03:46.840 --> 00:03:48.280
There's zero skin in this game.

00:03:48.680 --> 00:03:49.840
It's putting me to sleep.

00:03:50.199 --> 00:03:50.800
Let's bump it

00:03:51.000 --> 00:03:52.039
to 10,000 and actually

00:03:52.360 --> 00:03:53.280
make it interesting.

00:03:54.199 --> 00:03:54.759
Lan,

00:03:54.960 --> 00:03:55.719
we can swap you out

00:03:56.000 --> 00:03:57.240
if you're not up for it.

00:03:57.650 --> 00:03:58.439
- Nah.
- Seriously,

00:03:58.520 --> 00:03:59.759
we're playing for peanuts here.

00:04:00.260 --> 00:04:01.159
Who says I'm quitting?

00:04:01.840 --> 00:04:03.039
You do know

00:04:03.360 --> 00:04:03.840
that I live

00:04:04.080 --> 00:04:05.362
in the biggest villa

00:04:05.639 --> 00:04:06.599
at Longting One, right?

00:04:06.759 --> 00:04:07.840
I've got more than enough

00:04:08.000 --> 00:04:09.240
to cover your little bet.

00:04:09.360 --> 00:04:10.280
True, true.

00:04:10.599 --> 00:04:11.479
I could tell

00:04:11.479 --> 00:04:12.879
right away you were the real deal.

00:04:12.879 --> 00:04:13.560
Oh, absolutely.

00:04:14.460 --> 00:04:15.680
Let's stick to the usual, then.

00:04:15.919 --> 00:04:17.380
We settle the tab after every round.

00:04:17.599 --> 00:04:18.000
We good?

00:04:18.319 --> 00:04:19.120
Deal.

00:04:19.439 --> 00:04:19.960
Let's play.

00:04:22.330 --> 00:04:22.879
Eight Crack.

00:04:23.360 --> 00:04:24.079
I win.

00:04:24.639 --> 00:04:25.920
Hate to do it to you, Lan.

00:04:26.240 --> 00:04:27.560
I was waiting on that tile.

00:04:27.560 --> 00:04:28.759
Full Flush, Concealed,

00:04:28.759 --> 00:04:29.720
and a Hidden Quad.

00:04:30.160 --> 00:04:31.439
Let's see.

00:04:31.439 --> 00:04:32.439
That's 48 points,

00:04:32.959 --> 00:04:34.600
so 480,000. Much appreciated.

00:04:37.480 --> 00:04:38.079
It's okay, Lan.

00:04:39.199 --> 00:04:40.519
Nobody wins every hand.

00:04:40.780 --> 00:04:42.439
You were on such a streak
earlier anyway.

00:04:42.680 --> 00:04:43.800
This is just a blip.

00:04:44.160 --> 00:04:45.350
You'll make it up next round.

00:04:45.360 --> 00:04:45.920
Yeah.

00:04:46.600 --> 00:04:47.279
It's no big deal.

00:04:47.279 --> 00:04:48.100
Win some, lose some.

00:04:48.399 --> 00:04:48.759
Let's go.

00:04:49.439 --> 00:04:50.000
Next round.

00:05:00.120 --> 00:05:00.959
I win.

00:05:05.759 --> 00:05:06.839
I win.

00:05:08.199 --> 00:05:09.040
I win.

00:05:12.600 --> 00:05:13.600
I win.

00:05:26.199 --> 00:05:26.759
One Bamboo.

00:05:27.319 --> 00:05:28.560
Nobody needs this, right?

00:05:28.759 --> 00:05:29.959
- I win.
- I win.

00:05:30.199 --> 00:05:30.720
Seven Pairs.

00:05:30.730 --> 00:05:31.519
Big Three Dragons.

00:05:31.600 --> 00:05:32.639
13 Orphans.

00:05:33.079 --> 00:05:34.399
Triple Blast.

00:05:34.639 --> 00:05:36.120
180 points.

00:05:36.519 --> 00:05:38.759
That makes it 1,800,000.

00:05:39.480 --> 00:05:40.680
I'll take that.

00:05:41.759 --> 00:05:42.560
Lan,

00:05:43.399 --> 00:05:44.959
a few bad runs don't mean anything.

00:05:45.360 --> 00:05:47.079
You were up a million before this.

00:05:47.240 --> 00:05:48.000
Now Lan,

00:05:48.319 --> 00:05:49.639
time to settle up.

00:05:50.839 --> 00:05:52.240
Can I just put it on my tab for now?

00:05:52.800 --> 00:05:54.720
We agreed on the jump.

00:05:54.879 --> 00:05:56.879
We settle up every round.

00:05:57.519 --> 00:05:59.040
Weren't you the one preaching

00:05:59.060 --> 00:06:00.120
about being a good sport?

00:06:01.920 --> 00:06:02.399
Fine.

00:06:03.360 --> 00:06:04.000
I'll pay.

00:06:05.480 --> 00:06:06.160
I'll pay now.

00:06:12.337 --> 00:06:13.962
(Payment received: 1,800,000)

00:06:14.319 --> 00:06:14.720
Alright.

00:06:15.120 --> 00:06:15.959
Let's call it a day.

00:06:16.279 --> 00:06:16.700
I'm done.

00:06:16.959 --> 00:06:17.399
Hold on.

00:06:18.240 --> 00:06:19.319
I just paid up,

00:06:19.319 --> 00:06:20.240
and now you're leaving?

00:06:20.399 --> 00:06:20.959
Lan,

00:06:21.560 --> 00:06:23.000
it's not that we're calling it quits.

00:06:23.439 --> 00:06:25.000
It's just that you tapped out.

00:06:25.560 --> 00:06:25.879
I...

00:06:26.120 --> 00:06:26.560
Ms. Lan,

00:06:27.160 --> 00:06:28.800
looks like you're out of bankroll.

00:06:29.079 --> 00:06:29.439
Nonsense.

00:06:30.199 --> 00:06:30.879
I have money.

00:06:31.279 --> 00:06:33.720
I just don't have that much cash
on hand right now.

00:06:35.560 --> 00:06:36.600
Hongyan, please.

00:06:36.800 --> 00:06:38.199
Could you lend me some?

00:06:38.199 --> 00:06:39.360
Lan, don't worry.

00:06:39.839 --> 00:06:41.319
Let me see what I can do.

00:06:41.680 --> 00:06:42.279
Okay.

00:06:44.360 --> 00:06:46.120
Ms. Lian, we're all friends here.

00:06:46.519 --> 00:06:48.319
Maybe you could cut Lan some slack?

00:06:49.862 --> 00:06:50.759
I'll make an exception.

00:06:50.759 --> 00:06:51.920
Just for your sake.

00:06:52.120 --> 00:06:52.639
I know.

00:06:53.240 --> 00:06:56.000
Lan, do you have anything
you could put up as collateral?

00:06:56.839 --> 00:06:58.279
I'll front you the cash if you do.

00:06:58.639 --> 00:06:59.040
I...

00:06:59.600 --> 00:07:01.720
How about that big villa of yours?

00:07:02.199 --> 00:07:03.040
Put it up.

00:07:03.480 --> 00:07:04.319
That's right.

00:07:04.759 --> 00:07:05.439
Lan, come on.

00:07:05.879 --> 00:07:07.279
You've got Longting One A05.

00:07:07.600 --> 00:07:09.120
That place is worth 180 million.

00:07:09.839 --> 00:07:11.199
But that belongs to Ye Chen.

00:07:11.600 --> 00:07:12.759
He's your son-in-law, right?

00:07:13.120 --> 00:07:14.390
Since when do you answer to him?

00:07:14.680 --> 00:07:15.680
You're the one in charge.

00:07:16.000 --> 00:07:16.639
Exactly.

00:07:17.230 --> 00:07:18.920
Besides, you're just trying
to break even.

00:07:19.637 --> 00:07:20.879
It's not like it's a sure loss.

00:07:21.319 --> 00:07:22.075
What's the problem?

00:07:23.160 --> 00:07:24.360
You know what?

00:07:24.639 --> 00:07:25.680
Forget I asked.

00:07:26.199 --> 00:07:26.839
No, I'm in.

00:07:27.560 --> 00:07:28.839
I'll put up the villa.

00:07:30.720 --> 00:07:31.360
Here. Sign this.

00:07:34.000 --> 00:07:34.959
To hell with the odds.

00:07:36.000 --> 00:07:37.439
There's no way I'm blowing it all.

00:07:38.675 --> 00:07:39.400
(Pledgor: Ma Lan)

00:07:40.550 --> 00:07:42.262
(Pledgor: Ma Lan)

00:07:44.560 --> 00:07:44.959
Alright.

00:07:46.120 --> 00:07:46.639
Game on.

00:07:46.839 --> 00:07:47.519
Come on.

00:07:47.519 --> 00:07:48.399
Keep them coming.

00:07:48.399 --> 00:07:49.279
Let's go.

00:07:56.079 --> 00:07:56.839
Lan,

00:07:57.079 --> 00:07:58.279
this is awkward.

00:07:58.920 --> 00:08:01.040
You lost the entire 180 million.

00:08:01.519 --> 00:08:03.600
We have two ways to settle this.

00:08:04.560 --> 00:08:05.079
First, pay me

00:08:05.399 --> 00:08:06.279
100 million in cash.

00:08:08.199 --> 00:08:09.560
I don't have that kind of money.

00:08:11.070 --> 00:08:12.399
You're down to one option, then.

00:08:12.959 --> 00:08:15.759
Get your son-in-law here
to hand over the deed.

00:08:20.360 --> 00:08:21.079
No.

00:08:21.560 --> 00:08:22.399
Ms. Lian, please.

00:08:22.820 --> 00:08:24.720
You already took me
for more than two million.

00:08:25.000 --> 00:08:26.000
Don't take the villa,

00:08:26.000 --> 00:08:26.600
please.

00:08:27.360 --> 00:08:28.399
Trying to back out now?

00:08:28.839 --> 00:08:29.439
Careful.

00:08:29.962 --> 00:08:31.759
Don't make me do this the hard way.

00:08:33.279 --> 00:08:34.000
Hongyan.

00:08:36.040 --> 00:08:37.360
Help me out and talk to her.

00:08:37.360 --> 00:08:38.320
She's your friend, right?

00:08:38.320 --> 00:08:39.725
You said she's loaded.

00:08:39.879 --> 00:08:41.159
This is pocket change to her.

00:08:41.159 --> 00:08:42.039
I'm begging you!

00:08:42.039 --> 00:08:43.159
Hongyan, please!

00:08:43.159 --> 00:08:44.039
Look,

00:08:44.200 --> 00:08:45.399
you dug this hole.

00:08:45.679 --> 00:08:46.919
What am I supposed to do?

00:08:47.120 --> 00:08:48.080
But...

00:08:48.080 --> 00:08:48.679
Ms. Lian,

00:08:48.919 --> 00:08:49.679
I'm begging you!

00:08:49.679 --> 00:08:50.279
Have mercy

00:08:50.279 --> 00:08:50.759
on me!

00:08:51.039 --> 00:08:51.480
Please,

00:08:51.840 --> 00:08:52.519
have a heart!

00:08:52.519 --> 00:08:53.180
Spare me the act.

00:08:54.080 --> 00:08:55.039
I'm done being patient.

00:08:57.070 --> 00:08:57.960
We gave you an out.

00:08:58.679 --> 00:08:59.679
Don't push your luck!

00:09:00.390 --> 00:09:01.320
I don't have the money.

00:09:02.559 --> 00:09:03.879
I really don't.

00:09:05.080 --> 00:09:06.679
My life is all I've got left.

00:09:08.919 --> 00:09:09.879
I don't want your life.

00:09:10.240 --> 00:09:10.960
I want the money.

00:09:15.679 --> 00:09:17.039
What are you guys doing?

00:09:17.039 --> 00:09:17.559
Let me go!

00:09:17.879 --> 00:09:19.080
Hongyan, help me!

00:09:19.240 --> 00:09:20.080
What are you doing?

00:09:20.240 --> 00:09:21.000
Let go of me!

00:09:21.000 --> 00:09:21.559
Let go!

00:09:22.120 --> 00:09:22.879
I said let go!

00:09:23.399 --> 00:09:24.679
Hello? I'm talking to you.

00:09:25.120 --> 00:09:26.200
Don't make me say it again!

00:09:26.679 --> 00:09:27.360
Hurry up!

00:09:27.840 --> 00:09:28.279
Strip!

00:09:29.080 --> 00:09:31.320
Do it yourself, or we'll do it for you!

00:09:36.159 --> 00:09:37.039
Get on with it!

00:09:38.240 --> 00:09:39.120
Take it off!

00:09:41.679 --> 00:09:42.360
Keep going.

00:09:51.600 --> 00:09:52.320
Don't stop.

00:09:53.399 --> 00:09:54.200
There we go.

00:10:02.187 --> 00:10:05.475
(Name: Ma Lan)

00:10:08.720 --> 00:10:11.000
Wow, Lan, you've got quite the figure.

00:10:11.600 --> 00:10:12.919
If these get posted online,

00:10:13.080 --> 00:10:14.480
you'll go viral overnight.

00:10:19.159 --> 00:10:19.879
Lan,

00:10:20.159 --> 00:10:21.399
as one woman to another,

00:10:21.879 --> 00:10:22.639
I hate to...

00:10:23.639 --> 00:10:24.039
Relax.

00:10:25.000 --> 00:10:26.200
Tell you what, Lan.

00:10:26.600 --> 00:10:27.879
Here's another option for you.

00:10:28.799 --> 00:10:29.679
Go home and find

00:10:29.710 --> 00:10:31.360
this exact USB drive
your son-in-law has.

00:10:31.360 --> 00:10:31.960
Hand it over,

00:10:32.399 --> 00:10:33.240
and we're square.

00:10:34.039 --> 00:10:35.080
I'll delete the photos,

00:10:35.600 --> 00:10:36.759
and I won't take the villa.

00:10:37.240 --> 00:10:37.879
A USB drive?

00:10:38.960 --> 00:10:40.399
What's on it?

00:10:41.100 --> 00:10:42.890
You have much bigger things
to worry about.

00:10:43.399 --> 00:10:44.639
Like losing that villa,

00:10:45.000 --> 00:10:47.000
or the photos I have sitting
in that camera.

00:10:48.799 --> 00:10:49.600
Quit fumbling.

00:10:49.610 --> 00:10:50.639
I can post these anytime.

00:10:51.240 --> 00:10:52.320
No, don't.

00:10:54.080 --> 00:10:54.799
I'll do it.

00:10:55.380 --> 00:10:56.440
I'll go get it right now.

00:11:23.360 --> 00:11:24.279
Delete the photos,

00:11:24.770 --> 00:11:25.720
and I'll give it to you.

00:11:35.080 --> 00:11:36.440
What, you think you have leverage?

00:11:40.200 --> 00:11:41.000
Spray paint?

00:11:41.919 --> 00:11:42.960
You think I'm stupid?

00:11:43.399 --> 00:11:43.879
Qiang.

00:11:44.879 --> 00:11:45.879
You're pushing your luck.

00:11:46.000 --> 00:11:46.970
I'm the one you're after.

00:11:47.620 --> 00:11:48.519
Leave her out of this.

00:11:49.799 --> 00:11:50.399
Chen?

00:11:51.080 --> 00:11:51.559
Chen.

00:11:52.200 --> 00:11:54.390
I only did this because they have
indecent photos of me.

00:12:05.840 --> 00:12:07.080
The USB drive is with me.

00:12:08.559 --> 00:12:09.360
Right on cue.

00:12:09.690 --> 00:12:10.679
Hand over the USB drive.

00:12:10.919 --> 00:12:11.159
Now.

00:12:11.159 --> 00:12:11.799
Not a chance.

00:12:12.639 --> 00:12:13.120
Dream on.

00:12:14.240 --> 00:12:15.039
I know I messed up.

00:12:15.300 --> 00:12:16.919
But please, don't let those photos
get out.

00:12:16.919 --> 00:12:17.279
Mom,

00:12:18.080 --> 00:12:18.559
it's okay.

00:12:18.559 --> 00:12:19.090
I've got this.

00:12:19.720 --> 00:12:20.480
Oh really?

00:12:22.039 --> 00:12:22.919
You really want

00:12:22.919 --> 00:12:23.879
to make this difficult?

00:12:25.840 --> 00:12:28.279
I dare you to even try
laying your hands on him.

00:12:28.279 --> 00:12:29.879
What are Mr. Hong's men doing here?

00:12:30.525 --> 00:12:32.159
You must be tired of living

00:12:32.440 --> 00:12:33.919
if you're coming for him.

00:12:33.919 --> 00:12:35.159
We're sorry.

00:12:35.159 --> 00:12:36.279
Mr. Hong is expecting you.

00:12:36.480 --> 00:12:37.240
Get up!

00:12:37.399 --> 00:12:37.879
Hold on.

00:12:43.200 --> 00:12:44.919
This one's for my mother-in-law.

00:12:45.679 --> 00:12:46.720
- Now scram.
- Move!

00:12:50.039 --> 00:12:50.799
What do you want?

00:12:50.799 --> 00:12:51.600
Don't come any closer.

00:12:51.600 --> 00:12:52.360
Stay back!

00:12:52.480 --> 00:12:54.000
Your mother-in-law chose to play!

00:12:54.020 --> 00:12:54.960
And she knew the stakes!

00:12:55.120 --> 00:12:55.919
She even signed...

00:13:00.062 --> 00:13:02.120
I don't gamble,

00:13:03.039 --> 00:13:04.240
but I do play one game.

00:13:04.500 --> 00:13:05.360
Rock, paper, scissors.

00:13:06.039 --> 00:13:06.799
10 million a round.

00:13:07.679 --> 00:13:08.360
Shall we?

00:13:09.879 --> 00:13:10.559
10 million.

00:13:10.559 --> 00:13:11.279
20 million.

00:13:11.279 --> 00:13:12.000
30 million.

00:13:12.000 --> 00:13:12.720
40 million.

00:13:12.720 --> 00:13:13.440
50 million.

00:13:13.440 --> 00:13:13.960
60 million.

00:13:13.960 --> 00:13:14.480
70 million.

00:13:14.480 --> 00:13:15.159
80 million.

00:13:17.879 --> 00:13:18.279
Pay up.

00:13:19.200 --> 00:13:19.679
I'm sorry.

00:13:20.000 --> 00:13:21.600
I didn't know who I was dealing with.

00:13:21.600 --> 00:13:22.180
Just spare me.

00:13:22.559 --> 00:13:23.320
Please, have mercy.

00:13:23.320 --> 00:13:23.759
The villa?

00:13:23.759 --> 00:13:24.240
My hand, no.

00:13:25.120 --> 00:13:26.639
No, the villa is yours.

00:13:26.639 --> 00:13:28.200
Is her debt settled?

00:13:28.679 --> 00:13:29.159
Yes.

00:13:29.399 --> 00:13:30.000
All settled.

00:13:30.000 --> 00:13:30.720
You're sure?

00:13:30.720 --> 00:13:31.799
Yes, I swear.

00:13:31.799 --> 00:13:32.799
And the photos?

00:13:33.240 --> 00:13:34.240
The photos...

00:13:34.240 --> 00:13:35.200
They're right here.

00:13:40.639 --> 00:13:41.399
Any backups?

00:13:41.679 --> 00:13:43.360
No. None.

00:13:45.759 --> 00:13:46.240
Mom.

00:13:48.519 --> 00:13:49.600
I'll leave this to you.

00:14:13.519 --> 00:14:13.919
Mom.

00:14:15.679 --> 00:14:16.360
No one else

00:14:16.799 --> 00:14:18.159
will ever know about this.

00:14:19.559 --> 00:14:20.200
Chen.

00:14:21.320 --> 00:14:22.159
It's all my fault.

00:14:22.200 --> 00:14:23.799
You're my lifesaver.

00:14:24.360 --> 00:14:26.279
I've learned my lesson.

00:14:26.600 --> 00:14:28.159
No more gambling, I promise.

00:14:35.799 --> 00:14:37.240
So the table's rigged.

00:14:37.559 --> 00:14:39.240
You can pre-set every hand.

00:14:40.519 --> 00:14:42.120
No wonder I got cleaned out.

00:14:42.720 --> 00:14:44.399
You set me up.

00:14:45.240 --> 00:14:45.960
I looked into it.

00:14:46.879 --> 00:14:48.360
This isn't even your place.

00:14:49.200 --> 00:14:50.519
It's a rental, right?

00:14:52.799 --> 00:14:53.360
So tell me,

00:14:53.879 --> 00:14:55.279
how did you target my mother-in-law?

00:14:57.039 --> 00:14:58.120
Want to go again?

00:14:58.960 --> 00:14:59.987
It was her!

00:15:22.187 --> 00:15:24.675
♪They said I was only meant
to gaze at the light♪

00:15:24.762 --> 00:15:28.515
♪Never knowing I am the flame itself♪

00:15:28.975 --> 00:15:33.912
♪I am fireworks, not a fire cast aside♪

00:15:34.075 --> 00:15:36.362
♪I open my eyes amid the ruins♪

00:15:36.675 --> 00:15:39.355
♪No one shields me
from the wind or the sky♪

00:15:40.425 --> 00:15:43.050
♪Let them mock, let them sneer♪

00:15:43.350 --> 00:15:46.362
♪I sharpen my silence into blades♪

00:15:46.562 --> 00:15:49.612
♪Every cold word, I remember♪

00:15:49.725 --> 00:15:52.687
♪Etching my path of defiance
into my heart♪

00:15:52.955 --> 00:15:56.112
♪Fate did not sign my future for me♪

00:15:56.337 --> 00:16:00.087
♪I carved my own light
with clenched fists♪

00:16:00.087 --> 00:16:02.950
♪I belong to no one♪

00:16:03.012 --> 00:16:06.462
♪I am the ember
that refuses to bow to destiny♪

00:16:06.462 --> 00:16:09.137
♪Even if the world burns me into ash♪

00:16:09.137 --> 00:16:15.475
♪I will rise upon those ashes♪